text: Jhon González (born 29 August 1971) is a Colombian former cyclist. He competed in the men's sprint at the 1992 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1971 births Category:Living people Category:Colombian male cyclists Category:Olympic cyclists of Colombia Category:Cyclists at the 1992 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people) Category:Pan American Games medalists in cycling Category:Pan American Games bronze medalists for Colombia Category:Cyclists at the 1991 Pan American Games
